ably not that known globally), Morrowind and The Witcher 3. We really wanted to emphasize on player autonomy, instead of guiding systems like quest markers and minimaps.This results in an 「older」/more classical game experience compared to most modern RPGs.How do you like our design philosophy? What things do you like and/or don't like? And what are your favorite RPGs? Happy to hear from you!"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-693111bbe87e286e78897e51d780ac11_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "77 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2010673619001419372"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIsZrZnfiEwcRGEAMaCTExODU2MjM0OSCbl4TNBjAAOEpAFXITMjAxMDY3MzYxOTAwMTQxOTM3MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1774432504.918706", "card_id": "Q_271435202", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 5570}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你吃过最令人感动的食物是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-d43c70369e349004642311f23f8d8dd5_hd.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "74 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/271435202"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIsZrZnfiEwcRGEAMaCDIyNTkzODQyIJTDo9YFMAA40s0BQBZyCTI3MTQzNTIwMngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "23_1774432504.919089", "card_id": "Q_2019842508268515358", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 239}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "Token 正式被译名为「词元」，怎样看待这一翻译？「词元」到底是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "前段时间，养过「龙虾」的你可能对 Token 并不陌生。在 23 日举行的中国发展高层论坛 2026 年年会上，国家数据局局长刘烈宏给出了一个清晰的定位：Token「词元」不仅是智能时代的价值锚点，更是连接技术供给与商业需求的「结算单位」，为商业模式的落地提供了可量化的可能。这也从官方角度上为 Token 给出了翻译：词元。 更多资讯请下载央视新闻客户端 AI 热潮中，一个概念的地位正在渐渐凸显——Token，它是排行榜上大模型调用量的评估标准，也是大模型厂商销售套餐的计费单位。 日前在中国发展高层论坛 2026 年年会上，国家数据局局长刘烈宏表示，Token「词元」不仅是智能时代的价值锚点，更是连接技术供给与商业需求的「结算单位」，为商业模式的落地提供了可量化的可能；也从官方角度上为 Token 给出了翻译：「词元」。 他指出，2024 年年初，中国日均 Token 调用量为 1000 亿；到 2025 年底，跃升至 100 万亿；今年 3 月，已突破 140 万亿，两年增长超千倍。今年 1 月底以来，有的模型企业创下 20 天收入超越 2025 年全年总收入的业绩纪录。这组数字背后，是一套以 Token 计费为基础的新型商业逻辑正在加速演进。 "}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-ac1622478302031fef850b0f352be4ea.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "74 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2019842508268515358"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIsZrZnfiEwcRGEAMaCTExODg4MzQ4MiDMzYnOBjAAOPADQBdyEzIwMTk4NDI1MDgyNjg1MTUzNTh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "24_1774432504.920113", "card_id": "Q_2019856254051329471", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 30}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价 2026 年 3 月米哈游《崩坏星穹铁道》4.1 版本剧情任务「献给破晓的失控」？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "[图片]"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-4e3f00d9c0ec65700c916275d9416f75_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "71 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2019856254051329471"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIsZrZnfiEwcRGEAMaCTExODg4NDAwNyCa54nOBjAAOCJAGHITMjAxOTg1NjI1NDA1MTMyOTQ3MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "25_1774432504.920448", "card_id": "Q_36203397", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 42}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "计算机图形学的就业前景怎么样？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "很想了解一下这个行业，觉得图形这方面很有意思，而且能在视觉上看到自己的成果应该也是很高兴的一件事情吧。 可否请各位业内人士详细说下一些细分的研究方向、就业去向呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-68efcf224cd73f705e75c3ddcec1df4a_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "69 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/36203397"}}, "attached_info": "Cj0IsZrZnfiEwcRGEAMaBzY2ODgzNjMg2YDJsAUwADjUC0AZcggzNjIwMzM5N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "26_1774432504.920949", "card_id": "Q_667304444", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 21}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "抗战时期我国民兵常用的大刀，放在冷兵器时代算不算一款先进的武器？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "中世纪呢?"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-a49010c41ba004e218e19f69e43a299d_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "67 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/667304444"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IsZrZnfiEwcRGEAMaCTExMDU2NzU4NCDrzp63BjAAOBlAGnIJNjY3MzA0NDQ0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1774432504.921265", "card_id": "Q_2019790617547391900", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 49}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "多地宣布取消家长护学岗，教师成护学岗主力，这会影响老师的正常教学吗？护学岗到底应该由谁来负责？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近期，广东、广西、浙江、江苏等地部分学校相继取消或暂停家长护学岗，原本为减轻家长负担的举措，却让一线教师被迫承担起校园门前安全维护、交通疏导等护学工作。 记者了解到的多个方案中，除去保安、民警等人员，一线教师也被分派了工作。多位教师反映，护学需提前到岗、延后下班，义务执勤且无专业培训，还要应对家长沟通、秩序维护等工作，不仅拉长工作时间，更影响备课、批改作业等正常教学任务，甚至要承担失责风险。 教育学者熊丙奇告诉记者，护学岗属于社会事务，强制要求家长参加显然不合理。而要求学校负责校门外的安全管理工作，某种程度上也超出了学校的职责范围。无疑会增加教师的非教学负担，违背了为教师减负的要求。 2017 年，《国务院办公厅关于加强中小学幼儿园安全风险防控体系建设的意见》中明确提出，在学生安全区域内，公安机关要健全日常巡逻防控制度，加强学校周边「护学岗」建设，完善高峰勤务机制，优先布设视频监控系统，增强学生的安全感。 但在现实层面，一些地区确实警力有限，需要社会力量的补充。记者也注意到，近期以来，部分地区将街道、社区等工作人员纳入了护学工作。 相关链接：家长退出护学岗，老师干起了保安"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-934e2377476ae81d43adb9cec753cbd3.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2019790617547391900"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIsZrZnfiEwcRGEAMaCTExODg4MTE3NSD57IjOBjAAOE5AG3ITMjAxOTc5MDYxNzU0NzM5MTkwMHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1774432504.922332", "card_id": "Q_1931456234277561770", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 18}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么古典音乐圈更强调童子功、神童效应、等级考试和师承关系？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "为什么古典音乐圈更强调童子功、神童效应、等级考试和师承关系？尤其是师承关系。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c8cdcbbdbe01df1e200c3226b39dabd3.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1931456234277561770"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIsZrZnfiEwcRGEAMaCTExNTkxOTgxOSCqtYPEBjAAOE5AHHITMTkzMTQ1NjIzNDI3NzU2MTc3MHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1774432504.922776", "card_id": "Q_2019217867418125281", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 21}, "target": {"title_area":